text: Aast, Pyrénées-Atlantiques is a commune in the Pyrénées-Atlantiques department in southwestern France. == Transport == === Road === The D311 and D64 roads pass through the commune. == Geography == Aast is on the border of the Pyrénées-Atlantiques department. ==Related pages== * Communes of the Pyrénées- Atlantiques department ==Other websites== *Aast on Google Maps *Aast on Géoportail, National Geographic Institute (IGN) website *Aast on the INSEE website Category:Communes in Pyrénées-Atlantiques
